ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectThe Selkirk Chamber of Commerce CHANGE NAME / BOUNDARIES
PrecisApproval to grant the application of the SELKIRK CHAMBER OF COMMERCE in Manitoba (a) to change its name to the SELKIRK AND DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE and (b) to change the boundaries of its district to crrespond to the rural municipalities of St. Clements, St. Andrews and West St. Paul.
